text: Pepe Guilavogui (born 2 June 1993) is a Guinean football midfielder who plays for Orihuela CF in Spain. ==Club career== ===FC ViOn Zlaté Moravce - Vráble=== Guilavogui made his professional Fortuna Liga debut for ViOn Zlaté MoravceFC ViOn Zlaté Moravce - Vráble - Spartak Myjava 1:2 (0:1) 16.07.2016, futbalnet.sk against Spartak Myjava on 16 July 2016. ==International career== Guilavogui represented the Guinea U20s at the 2016 Toulon Tournament.http://www.thefa.com/news/2016/May/23/guinea-report-230516 ==References== ==External links== * FC Spartak Trnava official club profile * Fortuna Liga profile * * Eurofotbal profile * Futbalnet profile Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Guinean footballers Category:Guinean expatriate footballers Category:Association football forwards Category:Rayo Vallecano B players Category:Atlético Madrid B players Category:FC Spartak Trnava players Category:FC ViOn Zlaté Moravce players Category:Stade Bordelais (football) players Category:Orihuela CF players Category:Slovak Super Liga players Category:2.
